{"tid":767214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李雯希出戰《廣告女皇》","createTime":"2018-08-04T09:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T10:55:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e21930f22834d46819ceedaf7bcd008c6fa26e47","tid":767214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180804/20468251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F20468251&d=FGY%2FvSnesoFgnZVOdr372%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5d4ed0df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F20468251&h=1df446b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180804/20468251</a><br />\n<br />\n李雯希出戰《廣告女皇》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV繼舉行《Good Night Show全民造星》選男神後，將舉行《廣告女皇》，從二十多位參賽者中選出一位得獎者獨得十萬元獎金和廣告合約。<br />\n<br />\n據悉明天面試中，除有數位落選港姐參加外，更有無綫兒童節目《Think Big天地》女主持李雯希參加。李雯希原名李雯珊，曾參加亞視《亞洲星光大道3》，14年參加《超級巨聲4》後加盟無綫。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n清晞誦一個仔夠晒數<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n《狂舞派3》10月開拍<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n李雯珊 正呀， 以前亞洲星光大道好鐘意佢。<br />\n<br />\n原來改咗名兼係無線， 完全唔知。"},{"pid":"c865608c11645eaa875c746cd4c70309cb757178","tid":767214,"uid":27605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"雯希正呀 日日都有睇thinkbig天地"}]}